{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01SgTpNcgbcX1vVS52YB2fcx","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01DZgPz4nJEvJfCeAx9nEmai","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Read Excel workbook sheets","subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt":"Read the Excel workbook at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx\n\nI need you to:\n1. List all sheet names in the workbook\n2. Read the full \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - all rows and columns\n3. Read the full \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet - all rows and columns\n\nUse Python with openpyxl to read the file. Print ALL data from both sheets including headers, all rows, all cell values. Do not truncate - I need every row.\n\nHere's the Python code to run:\n```python\nimport openpyxl\n\nwb = openpyxl.load_workbook(r'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx', data_only=True)\n\nprint(\"Sheet names:\", wb.sheetnames)\n\nprint(\"\\n=== VENDOR ANALYSIS ASSESSMENT SHEET ===\")\nws = wb['Vendor Analysis Assessment']\nfor row in ws.iter_rows():\n    row_data = [str(cell.value) if cell.value is not None else '' for cell in row]\n    if any(v != '' for v in row_data):\n        print([cell.coordinate for cell in row], row_data)\n\nprint(\"\\n=== TOP 3 OPPORTUNITIES SHEET ===\")\nws2 = wb['Top 3 Opportunities']\nfor row in ws2.iter_rows():\n    row_data = [str(cell.value) if cell.value is not None else '' for cell in row]\n    if any(v != '' for v in row_data):\n        print([cell.coordinate for cell in row], row_data)\n```\n\nReturn ALL the data printed - do not summarize or truncate. I need every single row from both sheets."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1902,"cache_read_input_tokens":14418,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1902,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"89f939ac-99b7-4385-906e-eea1dafe39b8","uuid":"15195e57-d81e-4ce3-ab46-a8f689ff20cb"}
{"type":"system","subtype":"task_started","task_id":"ac54f4c38664461d7","tool_use_id":"toolu_01DZgPz4nJEvJfCeAx9nEmai","description":"Read Excel workbook sheets","task_type":"local_agent","prompt":"Read the Excel workbook at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx\n\nI need you to:\n1. List all sheet names in the workbook\n2. Read the full \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - all rows and columns\n3. Read the full \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet - all rows and columns\n\nUse Python with openpyxl to read the file. Print ALL data from both sheets including headers, all rows, all cell values. Do not truncate - I need every row.\n\nHere's the Python code to run:\n```python\nimport openpyxl\n\nwb = openpyxl.load_workbook(r'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx', data_only=True)\n\nprint(\"Sheet names:\", wb.sheetnames)\n\nprint(\"\\n=== VENDOR ANALYSIS ASSESSMENT SHEET ===\")\nws = wb['Vendor Analysis Assessment']\nfor row in ws.iter_rows():\n    row_data = [str(cell.value) if cell.value is not None else '' for cell in row]\n    if any(v != '' for v in row_data):\n        print([cell.coordinate for cell in row], row_data)\n\nprint(\"\\n=== TOP 3 OPPORTUNITIES SHEET ===\")\nws2 = wb['Top 3 Opportunities']\nfor row in ws2.iter_rows():\n    row_data = [str(cell.value) if cell.value is not None else '' for cell in row]\n    if any(v != '' for v in row_data):\n        print([cell.coordinate for cell in row], row_data)\n```\n\nReturn ALL the data printed - do not summarize or truncate. I need every single row from both sheets.","uuid":"71f4f009-be2a-42b7-bf5a-73e04aedf384","session_id":"89f939ac-99b7-4385-906e-eea1dafe39b8"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Read the Excel workbook at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx\n\nI need you to:\n1. List all sheet names in the workbook\n2. Read the full \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - all rows and columns\n3. Read the full \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet - all rows and columns\n\nUse Python with openpyxl to read the file. Print ALL data from both sheets including headers, all rows, all cell values. Do not truncate - I need every row.\n\nHere's the Python code to run:\n```python\nimport openpyxl\n\nwb = openpyxl.load_workbook(r'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx', data_only=True)\n\nprint(\"Sheet names:\", wb.sheetnames)\n\nprint(\"\\n=== VENDOR ANALYSIS ASSESSMENT SHEET ===\")\nws = wb['Vendor Analysis Assessment']\nfor row in ws.iter_rows():\n    row_data = [str(cell.value) if cell.value is not None else '' for cell in row]\n    if any(v != '' for v in row_data):\n        print([cell.coordinate for cell in row], row_data)\n\nprint(\"\\n=== TOP 3 OPPORTUNITIES SHEET ===\")\nws2 = wb['Top 3 Opportunities']\nfor row in ws2.iter_rows():\n    row_data = [str(cell.value) if cell.value is not None else '' for cell in row]\n    if any(v != '' for v in row_data):\n        print([cell.coordinate for cell in row], row_data)\n```\n\nReturn ALL the data printed - do not summarize or truncate. I need every single row from both sheets."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01DZgPz4nJEvJfCeAx9nEmai","session_id":"89f939ac-99b7-4385-906e-eea1dafe39b8","uuid":"816c08ee-08ae-423f-941e-d01fc9489287","timestamp":"2026-03-22T16:59:50.074Z"}
