nd Office Space Portfolio | $828K fragmented across 8 co-working vendors; high duplication (Parallel Strategic). Consolidate to 1-2 preferred operators; renegotiate volume-based pricing. 15% reduction through preferred-operator terms saves $124K annually. | 124,175 |\n\n---\n\n**Summary:**\n- The workbook has **7 sheets** total: `Vendor Analysis Assessment`, `Top 3 Opportunities`, `Methodology`, `CEOCFO Recommendations`, `Config`, `First Quick Analysis`, `STEP08 Strategic Scores`\n- **Vendor Analysis Assessment**: 386 data rows (rows 2-387) plus a header row, with 6 columns (Vendor Name, Department, Cost, Description, Suggestion, DERIVED-Spend Category). The DERIVED-Spend Category column (F) is empty for all rows.\n- **Top 3 Opportunities**: 3 data rows (rows 2-4) plus a header row, with 4 columns. Combined estimated annual savings across all 3 opportunities: **$754,974**."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ac54f4c38664461d7 (use SendMessage with to: 'ac54f4c38664461d7' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 55719\ntool_uses: 9\nduration_ms: 325020</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"89f939ac-99b7-4385-906e-eea1dafe39b8","uuid":"411d2cd1-098e-4d9e-be47-c0216de31fec","timestamp":"2026-03-22T17:05:15.097Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the Excel workbook at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx\n\nI need you to:\n1. List all sheet names in the workbook\n2. Read the full \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - all rows and columns\n3. Read the full \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet - all rows and columns\n\nUse Python with openpyxl to read the file. Print ALL data from both sheets including headers, all rows, all cell values. Do not truncate - I need every row.\n\nHere's the Python code to run:\n```python\nimport openpyxl\n\nwb = openpyxl.load_workbook(r'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari)